{"tid":1296930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果真係成立獨立調查委員會咁多位連登仔有咩意見？","createTime":"2019-07-08T13:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:47:54.000Z","uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"21f6dc53cff1dbd7c21cf9198262078968589569","tid":1296930,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:38:17.000Z","msg":"容許我打個飛機先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先社會各界都要有個代表啦<br />\n我就咁諗 <br />\n建制：曾鈺成 雖然建制都係一班中共奴才嚟㗎啦、但係以表公正都要有一個，曾主席一直以黎都畀到市民公平嘅形象，睇佢喺立法會屌柒元秋就知，算係建制入面算係一舊無咁臭嘅屎<br />\n<br />\n泛民我就想係楊岳橋，楊律師無論係學識定能力方面喺泛民都算數一數二，相信都得到大家嘅認同<br />\n<br />\n警犬內部就求撚其啦 個個都一鳩樣 反正無一個係無辜 遲早清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位又有咩提議<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c551d7e3cf7fb93d37adc6fa70f40c1786e11278","tid":1296930,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:41:21.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e428135f48a6eebe61d70ef164193b887e7edb2","tid":1296930,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:42:08.000Z","msg":"無人肯同我一齊打飛機？係我諗得太天真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70125ea9da37d0563bf9c176c91be2f0a7430773","tid":1296930,"uid":156326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3e428135f48a6eebe61d70ef164193b887e7edb2","tid":1296930,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:42:08.000Z","msg":"無人肯同我一齊打飛機？係我諗得太天真？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:43:17.000Z","msg":"起色都未冇打乜春飛機姐"},{"pid":"3759b6c01f7d1f615f1a35c594731f7ec772f129","tid":1296930,"uid":184787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:43:47.000Z","msg":"加埋盧偉聰入去，係咁loop d克警濫用武力、幾廿人保護大媽、情緒失控既片，睇佢點兜"},{"pid":"e47b96b64c341931da23c1f63c8a484b